OL,3,C'Please be kind': Louise Thompson
OL,4,Cannounces she has had stoma bag fitted
OL,6,FReality TV personality Louise Thompson
OL,7,Fhas revealed she had a stoma bag after
OL,8,Fbeing diagnosed with ulcerative
OL,9,Fcolitis in 2018.
OL,11,FThe former star posted the news on
OL,12,FInstagram after previously sharing her
OL,13,Fongoing struggles with the bowel
OL,14,Fcondition.
OL,16,FIn a short video she lifted up her top
OL,17,Fto show the bag attached to her
OL,18,Fstomach alongside the caption: "HOW DO
OL,19,FI DISCLOSE THIS SORT OF NEWS?
