OL,3,C'Please be kind': Louise Thompson
OL,4,Cannounces she has had stoma bag fitted
OL,6,F"It's not exactly exciting like a big
OL,7,Fpregnancy or gender reveal
OL,8,Fannouncement! Hey look I'm having a
OL,9,Fboy... Hey look I've got a stoma!
OL,11,F"So I guess I'll just stand here.
OL,12,FProud in stature. With my new friend.
OL,13,FLe bum bag, that represents life. And
OL,14,Fhopefully a better one.
OL,16,F"Isn't it bizarre that this little
OL,17,Fgrey pouch is the price I pay for good
OL,18,Fhealth! I say good riddance to that
OL,19,Fnasty menacing colon! Please be kind."
