OL,6,FUlcerative colitis is a chronic bowel
OL,7,Fcondition where the colon and rectum
OL,8,Fbecome inflamed.
OL,10,FSmall ulcers can develop on the
OL,11,Fcolon's lining, and can bleed and
OL,12,Fproduce pus.
OL,14,FThe severity of the symptoms varies,
OL,15,Fdepending on how much of the rectum
OL,16,Fand colon is inflamed and how severe
OL,17,Fthe inflammation is.
OL,19,FFor some people, the condition has a
OL,20,Fsignificant impact on their everyday
OL,21,Flives.
