OL,6,FHow does a stoma bag help?
OL,8,FA stoma is an opening on the wall of
OL,9,Fthe stomach that brings your bowel to
OL,10,Fthe outside.
OL,12,FIf you have a stoma, the contents of
OL,13,Fyour gut do not travel all the way
OL,14,Fthrough your bowel to come out of your
OL,15,Fbottom. Instead, they come out of the
OL,16,Fstoma into a bag you wear.
