OL,3,C'Please be kind': Louise Thompson
OL,4,Cannounces she has had stoma bag fitted
OL,6,FIn February, Thompson spent more than
OL,7,Ftwo weeks in hospital after she became
OL,8,Fseriously ill with an undisclosed
OL,9,Fcondition while on holiday with her
OL,10,Ffamily in Antigua.
OL,12,FShe has previously been open about the
OL,13,Fhealth issues she has suffered since
OL,14,Fthe birth of her son, when she almost
OL,15,Fdied and was left with PTSD.
OL,17,FThompson appeared in Made In Chelsea's
OL,18,Ffirst series in 2011, progressing to
OL,19,Fbecome one of the E4 show's main
OL,20,Fcharacters.
